overview: The Busted Knuckle Crew is Back and the Sport of Rock Bouncing is Wilder than Ever. These full tube chassis Hotrods of the Rocks are tougher thanks to New Indestructible Drivetrain Parts. The Horsepower Numbers they are now putting to the ground will make any Bounty Hill tremble with Fear. And the Hills and Obstacles have been taken to a whole new level of Insanity! Go along for the ride of your life as we travel all over the Country following the Crazy Rock Stars of Rock Bouncing on an Epic quest to conquer the Baddest Hills and Obstacles known to man. Shot on location in Tennessee, Oklahoma, West Virginia, Alabama, and California. You won't find any Rock Crawling in Here! Just Wide Open, Rev Limiter Hitting, Rock Slinging CHAOS. This is the Rock Bouncing Film of the Year! Join us for this hour and a half long adrenaline rush that is suitable for all ages.
title: Rock Rods 5
